{"tid":1635330,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"請繼續嗌「五大訴求，缺一不可」，額外訴求請另嗌口號，勿混為一談成新訴求","createTime":"2019-10-07T13:03:41.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-07T16:26:39.000Z","uid":241093,"like":63,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"8a58d9ba119ffc518a6ba851b4b6beba9a3e2d63","tid":1635330,"uid":241093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:03:41.000Z","msg":"嗌咗三個月，社會一致共識、最核心嘅都係五大訴求<br />\n反蒙面法就一定要反，但請各手足另嗌一個口號<br />\n切匆混合一起最初的「五大」！<br />\n<br />\n呢「五大」係我哋運動最初嘅目標，深入民心<br />\n如果政府又實施另一項惡法，是否又變成「七大訴求」、「八大訴求」？<br />\n<br />\n大家唔好忘記，撤回監控燈柱都係我哋其中目標之一，咁係咪又加入成口號嘅「X大訴求」之一？<br />\n<br />\n點解十點窗邊嗌口號 而家少咗人嗌<br />\n係因為曾經提議改為九點<br />\n大家未曾有一個共識，<br />\n亂了方向，無法團結<br />\n變成「另類分化」<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">政府共匪就係想你哋咁<br />\n當大家口號唔一致，共識唔同，<br />\n軍心不穩，自然缺少凝聚力！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>請繼續保持五大訴求，缺一不可！</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e98da078d027328922c3ef24b728814f9701616","tid":1635330,"uid":241093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:10:53.000Z","msg":"自推十連之一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4e3fa50b4742005b554d4a8010988b1df5dc38ee","tid":1635330,"uid":241093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:15:01.000Z","msg":"自推十連之二<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7da4f3ab07b776248dc4c9182da38326252b990","tid":1635330,"uid":241093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T13:17:21.000Z","msg":"自推十連之三<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d91825e599cdcdaad4cc2adf0c6c12c5d0bedb