},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:09:53.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n最重要嘅係真普選<br />\n更多政府黑暗嘢去揭露<br />\n到時一定更多訴求<br />\n要嗌嘅請另嗌口號<br />\n勿模糊焦點<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b43dcf1689a3f3d7ffae4fa8d5c44fd6e41c2b66","tid":1635330,"uid":241093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:10:24.000Z","msg":"自推十連之六<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c3275ac5866e4d1cb1687fa03959e073ab74c68e","tid":1635330,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbee76127bdef782e8b8b2556e9b770b017bbc6f","tid":1635330,"uid":241093,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"c3275ac5866e4d1cb1687fa03959e073ab74c68e","tid":1635330,"uid":36478,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:10:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/censored.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:13:28.000Z","msg":"只會令其他國家認為貪得無厭<br />\n法國黃背心係一個好好例子<br />\n太多要求 間接令黃背心運動失去民眾支持<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9a2fc7747d2a7e8f5e1593c6ea06072ebb00f861","tid":1635330,"uid":143321,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T14:14:52.000Z","msg":"請繼續保持五大訴求，缺一不可！"}]}